title: File:Sector Baltimore change of command 120719-G-VC567-0073.jpg
author: Petty Officer 2nd Class Jonathan Lindberg
description: BALTIMORE - Capt. Kevin Kiefer, the new commander of Coast Guard Sector Baltimore, address the crowd during a change of command ceremony at the Baltimore Cruise Terminal here, July 19, 2012. Kiefer recently served as the chief of the Office of Port and Facility Compliance at Coast Guard Headquarters in Washington. U.S. Coast Guard photo by Petty Officer 3rd Class Jonathan Lindberg.
